Paper: hep-th/0009207

Date: 2000-09-26

Title: Brane tunneling and the Brane World scenario

Authors: Alexander Gorsky, Konstantin Selivanov

Comments: 13 pages, contribution to the Proceedings of E.S.Fradkin Memorial

Conference, Moscow, 2000Fate of branes in external fields is reviewed. Spontaneous creation of theBrane World in $AdS_{5}$ with external field is described. The resulting BraneWorld consists of a flat 4d spatially finite expanding Universe and curvedexpanding "regulator" branes. All branes have a positive tension.